Task: Implement core publishing logic: Upload images -> Replace URLs -> Create WeChat Draft
Summary: Implemented the Publisher class which orchestrates the publishing flow.
- Extracts images from Markdown.
- Uploads images to WeChat API.
- Replaces local image paths with remote URLs in the content.
- Creates a draft on WeChat.
- Validates that at least one image exists to serve as the thumbnail.
Files:
- src/publisher.ts
- tests/publisher.test.ts
Why: To enable users to publish their Obsidian notes directly to WeChat with images.
